  30 Jan 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org>
  +files/4.2-fPIC-python.patch, snns-4.2-r6.ebuild:
  added ~amd64 to -r6 and a patch which is required if USE=python. fixes #79773

